    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and drives well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable surface scratches and a small dent on the driver-side door. Inside, the upholstery exhibits some fading and minor wear on the bolsters, though all electronic components and the climate control system are fully operational. It is a solid, honest car that would benefit from a little cosmetic attention but is ready to hit the road as is.",
