    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it\u2019s always been garage-kept! It still has that 'new car' feel and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I\u2019d love for someone to enjoy it as much as I have, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
